offer made Successfully joining the offered job. </span></p><p class="brz-ff-montserrat brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-400 brz-fw-sm-im-400 brz-fw-xs-im-400"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Points earned will be transferred to your Vantage Circles Account. (Login information will be shared via email once registered). </span></p><p class="brz-ff-montserrat brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-400 brz-fw-sm-im-400 brz-fw-xs-im-400"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">1 Vantage point = INR 1 and 100 points = INR 100. </span></p><p class="brz-mt-lg-0 brz-mb-lg-0 brz-tp-paragraph brz-ff-montserrat brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-400 brz-fw-sm-im-400 brz-fw-xs-im-400"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Pride Circle reserves exclusive rights to modify the program policies as and when required.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="brz-accordion__item"><div class="brz-accordion__nav" data-collapsible="on"><span class="brz-span brz-text__editor">How do i access Vantage Circle Platform?</span></div><div class="brz-accordion__content"><div id class="brz-css-jtywf brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-d-xs-flex brz-css-dhrlp"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-css-fdpnq" data-custom-id="hlmmmmnfqkqbvnsnsprxhjmuwzyemduamppo"><p class="brz-fs-lg-16 brz-fs-sm-im-15 brz-fs-xs-im-15 brz-fw-lg-400 brz-fw-sm-im-400 brz-fw-xs-im-400">You will be provided with a login ID and password to access Vantage Circle Platform.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="br uF~U␀␀ uF~U␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀0.F~U␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀0F~U␀␀uF~U␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@uF~U␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@uF~U␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀_editor">Where can i view my points summary?</span></div><div class="brz-accordion__content"><div id class="brz-css-jtywf brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-d-xs-flex brz-css-dhrlp"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-css-fdpnq" data-custom-id="ogsvzxmryyctuwsxjkoesrztnaupkqsmrxxw"><p class="brz-lh-lg-1_9 brz-lh-sm-im-1_6 brz-lh-xs-im-1_6 brz-fs-lg-16 brz-fs-sm-im-15 brz-fs-xs-im-15 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-f